import React from 'react'
import {Box, Typography,Grid,TextField, Paper} from '@mui/material'
import { color } from '@mui/system'

export const Details = () => {
  return (
    <Box >
        <Grid container justifyContent={'center'}>
  <Grid item xs={4} md={8}  sx={{marginTop:4,boxShadow: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px'}}> 
  <Paper
   sx={{padding:'10px',height:'fit-content'}}
  >
  <Typography >Create Account</Typography>
       
 <Box mt={4}> 
  <Typography  sx={{fontSize:'15px',color:'#BB4C46',ml:1}}>Account Name</Typography>
  <Typography sx={{padding:'5px'}}><input type={'text'} style={{height:'30px',width:'300px',border:'1px solid #cccccc'}} />
 </Typography>
  </Box>
    
  <Box mt={4}> 
  <Typography  sx={{fontSize:'15px',ml:1}}>Account Code</Typography>
  <Typography sx={{padding:'5px'}}><input type={'text'} style={{height:'30px',width:'300px',border:'1px solid #cccccc'}} />
 </Typography>
  </Box>

  <Box mt={4}> 
  <Typography  sx={{fontSize:'15px',color:'#BB4C46',ml:1}}>Account Type</Typography>
  <Typography sx={{padding:'5px'}}><input type={'text'} style={{height:'30px',width:'300px',border:'1px solid #cccccc'}} />
 </Typography>
  </Box>

  

  <Box mt={4}> 
  <Typography  sx={{fontSize:'15px',ml:1}}>Description</Typography>
   <textarea rplaceholder="Max 500 characters" style={{color:'gray'}} > </textarea>
 
  </Box>
  </Paper> 
  </Grid>
</Grid>
        
        </Box>
  )
}
